{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"CSS Font Loading API","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSS_Font_Loading_API","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSS_Font_Loading_API\">CSS Font Loading API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSS_Font_Loading_API\"><code>CSS_Font_Loading_API</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>CSS Font Loading API 的相关页面</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Document/fonts\"><code>Document.fonts</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FontFace\"><code>FontFace</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FontFaceSet\"><code>FontFaceSet</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FontFaceSetLoadEvent\"><code>FontFaceSetLoadEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/fonts\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope.fonts</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>这是一个实验中的功能</strong><br>此功能某些浏览器尚在开发中，请参考<a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">浏览器兼容性表格</a>以得到在不同浏览器中适合使用的前缀。由于该功能对应的标准文档可能被重新修订，所以在未来版本的浏览器中该功能的语法和行为可能随之改变。</p></div>\n<p>CSS 字体加载 API 为您提供了动态加载字体资源时的 events 和 interfaces。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"interfaces","title":"Interfaces","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"fontface\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FontFace\"><code>FontFace</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>表示单个可用的字体。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"fontfaceset\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FontFaceSet\"><code>FontFaceSet</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>字体 API 的一个接口，支持检测它们（字体文件）的下载状态。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"fontfacesource\"><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此文档尚未被撰写，期待你的贡献!\"><code>FontFaceSource</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>提供混合了所有的字体相关操作，除非你别有深意。它定义了 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Document\"><code>Document</code></a> 和 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a> 中的可用属性 <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此文档尚未被撰写，期待你的贡献!\"><code>FontFaceSources.fonts</code></a> 。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"fontfacesetloadevent\"><code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Reference/Events/FontFaceSetLoadEvent\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">FontFaceSetLoadEvent</a></code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FontFaceSet\"><code>FontFaceSet</code></a> 加载时触发的事件。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-font-loading/#fontface-interface","title":"CSS Font Loading Module Level 3"}],"query":"api.FontFace"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.FontFace","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSS_Font_Loading_API/bcd.json"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Interfaces","id":"interfaces"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"}],"summary":"CSS 字体加载 API 为您提供了动态加载字体资源时的 events 和 interfaces。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"CSS Font Loading API","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"CSS Font Loading API","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"CSS Font Loading API","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/css_font_loading_api","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/css_font_loading_api/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/doc